data.description: Brand new roof on property!! Spread out in the spacious, light filled home.  Flexible Floor Plan with Bonus Room, now sewing room, that could be dining room, family room or a 4th bedroom.  Formal Living Room with Vaulted Ceiling and Ceiling Fans.   Kitchen and Nook that look out over the spacious backyard.  Kitchen with granite tile counters and storage.  Sliding door to backyard patio and fenced yard with Tool Shed.  Easy Access to Hwy 99W.  Great Views of the Coast Range from the Backyard.
